commentary: Tsotsobe to Misbah-ul-Haq, 1 run oh dear! Shehzad and Faf collide! Misbah steered it to the off side and they set off for a quick single, Faf ran in from point and dived towards the stumps just as Shehzad dived at the crease, Faf barged onto Shehhzad's chest and the batsman was struck on the chin too, Shehzad's mouth is bleeding, Faf is fine but Shehzad isn't.
